<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 06:16:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>日本企业预计中国2024年经济前景依然严峻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japanese-firms-expect-chinas-2024-economic-prospects-remain-grim-2024-01-15/</link><description>中国日本商工会议所周一发布的一份报告显示，在华日本企业预计今年世界第二大经济体的经济前景依然严峻。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 06:01:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japanese-firms-expect-chinas-2024-economic-prospects-remain-grim-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>阿拉斯加事故后，波音 737 MAX 向中国的交付面临新的延误 - 华尔街日报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-737-max-deliveries-china-face-fresh-delay-after-alaska-incident-wsj-2024-01-15/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》周日报道，本月阿拉斯加航空 MAX 9 飞机的一块面板在空中爆炸后，波音公司在恢复向中国交付 737 MAX 飞机方面面临着新的延迟。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 05:35:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-737-max-deliveries-china-face-fresh-delay-after-alaska-incident-wsj-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：朝鲜为什么要测试高超音速导弹以及它们是如何工作的？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/why-is-north-korea-testing-hypersonic-missiles-how-do-they-work-2024-01-15/</link><description>朝鲜周一表示，在对难以探测和拦截的下一代远程火箭的激烈竞争中，它已经测试了一种新型中程固体燃料高超音速导弹。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 05:31:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/why-is-north-korea-testing-hypersonic-missiles-how-do-they-work-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国呼吁召开加沙和平会议；哈马斯将透露以色列人质的命运</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/china-calls-gaza-peace-conference-hamas-disclose-fate-israeli-hostages-2024-01-15/</link><description>中国呼吁就加沙战争召开大规模、权威的和平会议，而激进组织哈马斯则播放了三名以色列人质的视频，并表示他们的命运将于周一公布。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 04:57:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/china-calls-gaza-peace-conference-hamas-disclose-fate-israeli-hostages-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：市场应对北京对台湾的不满</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-01-15/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 04:37:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国光大集团前董事长因涉嫌腐败被捕 - 官方媒体</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-everbright-group-chairman-arrested-suspicion-corruption-state-media-2024-01-15/</link><description>官方媒体周一援引中国最高检察官的消息称，国有金融集团中国光大集团前董事长唐双宁因涉嫌受贿和腐败被捕。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 03:38:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-everbright-group-chairman-arrested-suspicion-corruption-state-media-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>美国前官员称对台湾的承诺“坚如磐石”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-says-commitment-taiwan-rock-solid-looks-forward-continuity-2024-01-15/</link><description>一位前美国高级官员周一对台湾总统蔡英文表示，美国期待台湾新政府领导下的台美关系保持连续性，美国对台湾的承诺“坚如磐石”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 03:35:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-says-commitment-taiwan-rock-solid-looks-forward-continuity-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>新疆雪崩滞留游客被直升机救起</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/tourists-stranded-by-avalanches-chinas-xinjiang-lifted-safety-by-helicopter-2024-01-15/</link><description>据当地媒体周日报道，通往中国西北地区新疆热门冬季旅游区的高速公路遭遇雪崩，一些滞留数日的游客被直升机送往安全地带。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 03:04:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/tourists-stranded-by-avalanches-chinas-xinjiang-lifted-safety-by-helicopter-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市落后于日经指数的上涨，中国跳过降息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-15/</link><description>对于执政党在台湾获胜的反应有限，基本上维持了现状。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 00:33:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国军方和政府不顾美国禁令采购英伟达芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-military-government-acquire-nvidia-chips-despite-us-ban-2024-01-14/</link><description>Nvidia 构建的图形处理单元被认为优于人工智能工作的竞争对手产品，因为它们可以更有效地处理机器学习任务所需的大量数据。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 23:08:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-military-government-acquire-nvidia-chips-despite-us-ban-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>瑞士外交官表示，结束乌克兰战争需要俄罗斯的盟友中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/top-diplomats-meet-davos-ukraine-peace-formula-2024-01-14/</link><description>乌克兰在达沃斯世界经济论坛上召开了来自世界各地的国家安全顾问会议，推动其和平方案结束与俄罗斯近两年的战争。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 12:13:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/top-diplomats-meet-davos-ukraine-peace-formula-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交官谴责外国政府就台湾大选后发表的言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-embassies-condemn-foreign-officials-over-taiwan-post-election-remarks-2024-01-14/</link><description>中国外交部及其驻世界各地的大使馆谴责外国政府在周六选举后祝贺台湾民进党及其当选总统赖清德。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 07:56:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-embassies-condemn-foreign-officials-over-taiwan-post-election-remarks-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>台湾新总统面临中国压力，未获得多数席位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-new-president-faces-tough-time-with-china-pressure-no-parliament-2024-01-14/</link><description>赖清德虽然以不到一半的选票以微弱优势获胜，但他的政党失去了对议会的控制权，当选总统将不得不依靠议会来通过立法和支出。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 06:20:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-new-president-faces-tough-time-with-china-pressure-no-parliament-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>中方反对日方向台湾当选总统贺电</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japans-congratulatory-message-taiwan-president-elect-2024-01-14/</link><description>中国驻日本大使馆周日表示，“坚决反对”日本外务大臣上川洋子祝贺台湾新当选总统赖清德的声明。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 04:19:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japans-congratulatory-message-taiwan-president-elect-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>台湾新当选总统赖清德将面临中国的愤怒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-president-elect-lai-face-chinas-ire-after-victory-2024-01-13/</link><description>赖在竞选期间多次表示，他希望与中国保持现状，并提出与北京对话。但在北京看来，他是一个分裂主义者，是一个“彻头彻尾的麻烦制造者”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 13:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-president-elect-lai-face-chinas-ire-after-victory-2024-01-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>